<h1>Payout Initiated</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @seller.display_name %>,</p>

<p>Great news! The buyer has completed payment for your <strong><%= @listing.brand_name %></strong> gift card.</p>

<div style="background: #d1fae5; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #065f46;"><strong>Your payout of <%= number_to_currency(@transaction.seller_payout) %> is on its way!</strong></p>
</div>

<div style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p><strong>Sale Summary:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Card Sold: <%= @listing.brand_name %> Gift Card (<%= number_to_currency(@listing.balance) %> value)</li>
    <li>Sale Price: <%= number_to_currency(@transaction.amount) %></li>
    <li>Platform Fee: <%= number_to_currency(@transaction.platform_fee) %></li>
    <li>Your Payout: <%= number_to_currency(@transaction.seller_payout) %></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>Funds typically arrive within 2-3 business days.</p>

<p>Thank you for selling on Cardly!</p>
